prodNameC: 拜爾斯達光學免疫法B型鏈球菌測定試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagent 1A-3.8mL:
Extraction Reagent 1A, Sodium Hypochlorite(<15% available chlorine).
Reagent 1B-3.8mL:
Extraction Reagent 1B, 0.5M Acetic Acid and yellow dye.
Reagent 2-3.6mL:
Neutralization Reagent, pH7.3: 1.5M MOPSO (3-[N-Morpholino]-2-hydroxypropanesulphonic acid), 20mM EGTA, 0.2% Tween® 20 detergent,blue dye, and Protein Stabilizer.
Reagent 3-3.6mL:
Conjugate, Buffered Anti-group B streptococcus antibody (rabbit) conjugated to Horseradish Peroxidase (HRP).
Reagent 4-125mL:
Wash Solution.
Test Devices-30ea.:
Surface coated with Anti-group B Streptococcus antibody (rabbit).
Postive Control-0.7mL:
Purified strep B streptococcal antigen.
Extraction Tubes-30ea.:
Dried Sodium Nitrite (NaNO2) with blue dye.
Transfer Pipettes-30ea.
Swabs-30ea.:
Sterile Rayon swab.
applicantAddr: 新北市永和區中山路一段174號11樓
efficacy: 快速偵測在子宮頸及陰道拭子檢體中B型鏈球菌之抗原。

mdKind.mdKindMCodeName: C 免疫學及微生物學用裝置
